Sylvania, Aquarius to Explore for Platinum Group Metals at Everest North

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-03T06:04:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-03/sylvania-aquarius-to-explore-for-platinum-group-metals-at-everest-north.html
Sylvania Platinum Ltd. said it has
entered into an agreement with  Aquarius Platinum Ltd. (AQP)  to examine
the feasibility of extracting and processing platinum group
metal-bearing ore from the Everest North deposit in  South
Africa .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
